com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.wizard

Interface ISCUIWizardFlowController

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SCUIDefaultWizardController

    public interface ISCUIWizardFlowController
    This interface defined a processRequest method which all wizard controllers should implement in order to server wizard requests. Framework has provided a default implementation of this interface SCUIDefaultWizardController.
    Note: Make sure to write the implementation thread safe implementation. asmishra

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      SCUIWizardControllerResponse processRequest(SCUIWizardMetaData wizardMetaData, SCUIContext uiContext)
      This method should handle all wizard requests.

    • Method Detail

      • processRequest

        SCUIWizardControllerResponse processRequest(SCUIWizardMetaData wizardMetaData,
                                            SCUIContext uiContext)
                                     throws java.lang.Exception
        This method should handle all wizard requests. This method should should determine the type of call (start, next, previous, finish or cancel), wizard definition id, next page. And based on the next page, this method should return a SCUIWizardControllerResponse with URI as the next page to which the request would either be forwarded to or included. wizardMetaData uiContext wizard controller response
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
